cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.SE 

This paper discusses the challenges of security and privacy in IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also presents a Python library for IoT developers, which involves networking and communication protocols (cs.IR), as well as network infrastructure and protocols (cs.NI). The library is designed to improve privacy and reduce bandwidth overhead, which relates to system and control theory (cs.SY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
